(6, 1, '2018-01-22 22:15:53', '2018-01-22 21:15:53', '<div  data-label=\"Features\" data-id=\"features-13\" data-export-id=\"features-13\" data-category=\"features\" class=\"features-13 content-section content-section-spacing\" id=\"features-5\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-image: none;\"> <div  class=\"\"> <div  class=\"row text-center\"> <div  class=\"section-title-col\" data-type=\"column\"> <h2  class=\"\">  Propos </h2> <p  class=\"lead\">Elyses Nails Paris, est situe au centre du 8eme arrondissement de Paris  500 mtres du Palais de lElyses et de Htel palace Le Bristol. Et bien sur  deux pas des Champs Elyses, place de Concorde et place saint Augustin. <br ><br >Salon de manucure deco moderne et design hyper tendance, chic et sophistique. Avec 3 postes de Manucures, 2 fauteuils pour la beaut des pieds et une cabine de soins ddie aux epilations  la cire.&nbsp;</p> </div> </div> <div  class=\"row spaced-cols\" data-type=\"row\"> <div  class=\"col col-sm-6 col-md-3 space-bottom\"><img  class=\"custom-image\" src=\"https://mvle.fr/elyseenails/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/cropped-Merry_Christmas_03-4.png\">     </div> <div  class=\"col col-sm-6 col-md-3 space-bottom\"><img  class=\"custom-image\" src=\"https://mvle.fr/elyseenails/wp-content/uploads/cropped-sample_02-3.jpg\">     </div> <div  class=\"col col-sm-6 col-md-3 space-bottom\"><img  class=\"custom-image\" src=\"https://mvle.fr/elyseenails/wp-content/uploads/cropped-sample_01.jpg\">     </div> <div  class=\"col col-sm-6 col-md-3 space-bottom\"><img  class=\"custom-image\" src=\"https://mvle.fr/elyseenails/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/cropped-215602f2c2944bb252fd882a5bd67e84-chinese-paints-1.jpg\">     </div> </div> </div> </div><div  data-label=\"Features\" data-id=\"features-16\" data-export-id=\"features-16\" data-category=\"features\" class=\"features-16 content-section content-section-spacing\" id=\"features-9\" style=\"background-color: #f5fafd;\">\n<div  class=\"gridContainer\">