">\n<div  class=\"row text-center\">\n<div  class=\"section-title-col\" data-type=\"column\">\n<h2  class=\"\">Nos Produits</h2>\n<p  class=\"lead\">Nous vous proposons, des soins de manucures hauts de gammes sur mesures pour vous aux meilleurs prix.<br >Avec la gamme de produits OPI nouvelle collection et des quipements de dernire gnration.</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"row spaced-cols\" data-type=\"row\">\n<div  class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-4 space-bottom\">\n\n<img  class=\"face\" src=\"https://mvle.fr/elyseenails/wp-content/uploads/v2.i1191484.w341.h200.x03746949.png\">\n<div  data-type=\"column\" class=\"col-padding-small col-padding-small-xs description-container\">\n\n\n\n\n<img  class=\"custom-image\" src=\"https://mvle.fr/elyseenails/wp-content/uploads/marque-opi-01.jpg\"><a  class=\"read-more\" href=\"https://www.opi.com\" target=\"_blank\" data-cp-link=\"1\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"position: relative; top: 0px; left: 0px;\">Visiter le site</a></div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-4 space-bottom\">\n\n<img  class=\"face\" src=\"https://mvle.fr/elyseenails/wp-content/uploads/v2.i1052846.w197.h40.x4A0A4FF4.png\">\n<div  data-type=\"column\" class=\"col-padding-small col-padding-small-xs description-container\">\n\n\n\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-4 space-bottom\">\n\n<img  class=\"face\" src=\"https://mvle.fr/elyseenails/wp-content/uploads/v2.i1156836.w229.h40.png\">\n<div  data-type=\"column\" class=\"col-padding-small col-padding-small-xs description-container\">\n\n\n\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div  id=\"testimonials-5\" style=\"background-color: #ffffff;\" data-label=\"Testimonials\" data-id=\"testimonials-5\" data-export-id=\"testimonials-5\" data-category=\"testimonials\" class=\"testimonials-5 content-section content-section-spacing\">\n<div  class=\"gridContainer\">\n<div  class=\"row\">\n<div  data-type=\"column\" class=\"section-title-col\">\n<h2  class=\"\">Nos Clients</h2>\n<p  class=\"lead\">Nous vous prvilligeons la qualit qui prime sur la quantit, telle est notre devise!</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"row spaced-cols content-center-sm\" data-type=\"row\">\n<div  class=\"col-sm-4\">\n<div  class=\"card y-move bordered\" data-type=\"column\">\n\n<i  class=\"fa icon color1 fa-quote-left small\"></i>\n<p  class=\"text-center\">Super quipe !!! Jai fait la pose rsine et vernis semi permanent la qualit est super et il y a un large choix de couleur,\n\nje recommande  100%\n\n\n</p>\n<img  src=\"https://mvle.fr/elyseenails/wp-content/uploads/cropped-avatar-00-1.png\" class=\"round icon\">\n<h6  class=\"\">Dely Margaux</h6>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"col-sm-4\">\n<div  class=\"card y-move bordered\" data-type=\"column\">\n\n<i  class=\"fa icon color1 fa-quote-left small\"></i>\n<p  class=\"text-center\">Jai apprci ma visite dans ce salon et je le recommande vivement\nDeco tres soigne ambiance chaleureuse et manucure trs bien ralise</p>\n<img  src=\"https://mvle.fr/elyseenails/wp-content/uploads/cropped-avatar-01-2.png\" class=\"round icon\">\n<h6  class=\"\">Lacondemine</h6>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"col-sm-4\">\n<div  class=\"card y-move bordered\" data-type=\"column\">\n\n<i  class=\"fa icon color1 fa-quote-left small\"></i>\n<p  class=\"text-center\">Petit salon de quartier trs mignon, dcor avec got, patron et employes adorable. Manucure bien faite, le travail nest pas fait  la chaine et cest agrable !&nbsp;&nbsp;Je recommande</p>\n<img  src=\"https://mvle.fr/elyseenails/wp-content/uploads/cropped-avatar-02-1.png\" class=\"round icon\">\n<h6  class=\"\">Camille</h6>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div  data-label=\"Features\" data-id=\"features-12\" data-export-id=\"features-12\" data-category=\"features\" class=\"features-12 content-section content-section-spacing \" id=\"features-1\" style=\"background-color: #f5fafd;\">\n<div  class=\"gridContainer\">\n<div  class=\"row text-center\">\n<div  class=\"section-title-col\" data-type=\"column\">\n<h2  class=\"\">Nos Prestations</h2>\n<p  class=\"lead\">Les soins raliss par des professionnels diplms qui sont l pour vous faire un agrable moment priviligi de dtente.\nLembellissement de vos ongles et vos mains et pieds avec, une garantie de travail dexcellence pour les rendre impeccable.</p></div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"row spaced-cols\" data-type=\"row\">\n<div  class=\"col-sm-6 col-md-6 \">\n<div  class=\"row space-bottom\">\n<div  class=\"col-sm-fit icon-column\"><i  class=\"fa icon color2 fa-mars bordered round\"> </i></div>\n<div  class=\"col-sm\" data-type=\"column\">\n<h5  class=\"color2\">BEAUT DES MAINS POUR HOMME</h5>\n<p  class=\"\">Manucure</p>\n\n<h6  class=\"\">23</h6>\n<h4  class=\"\">25m-30m</h4>\n<p  class=\"\">Beaut des pieds</p>\n\n<h6  class=\"\">35</h6>\n<h4  class=\"\">5m-40m</h4>\n<p  class=\"\">Beaut des mains + pieds</p>\n\n<h6  class=\"\">53</h6>\n<h4  class=\"\">1h-1h15m</h4>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"col-sm-6 col-md-6 \">\n<div  class=\"row space-bottom\">\n<div  class=\"col-sm-fit icon-column\"><i  class=\"fa icon color2 fa-delicious bordered round\"> </i></div>\n<div  class=\"col-sm\" data-type=\"column\">\n<h5  class=\"color2\">SOIN DES MAINS / HAND CARE</h5>\n<p  class=\"\">Beaut des pieds + vernis OPI</p>\n\n<h6  class=\"\">27</h6>\n<h4  class=\"\">35m-40m</h4>\n<p  class=\"\">Beaut des mains + semi permanente (dpose)</p>\n\n<h6  class=\"\">40/43</h6>\n<h4  class=\"\">30m-40m</h4>\n<p  class=\"\">Pose semi permanente french ou vernis french</p>\n\n<h6  class=\"\">+5</h6>\n<h4  class=\"\"><span  style=\"font-size: 16px; text-align: left;\">10m</span></h4>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"col-sm-6 col-md-6 \">\n<div  class=\"row space-bottom\">\n<div  class=\"col-sm-fit icon-column\"><i  class=\"fa icon fa-cube round bordered color2\"> </i></div>\n<div  class=\"col-sm\" data-type=\"column\">\n<h5  class=\"color2\">SOINS DES PIEDS / FOOT CARE</h5>\n<p  class=\"\">Beaut des pieds + ve